   "source": "## Configuration\n\nThe mapping below follows the requested sector-to-PCE-line choices. Sectors not listed in `BTOS_TO_PCE_LINE` are excluded. Sector 44 is omitted because it was not part of the supplied mapping.\n\n`BTOS_DATE_BASIS = \"collection\"` means the monthly bucket is based on the midpoint between `Collection Start`/`Col Start` and `Col End`. Change it to `\"reference\"` if you want the midpoint of the reference period instead.\n"
